\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=d8d64e16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>  。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：下午4時至凌晨1時；星期六、日及公眾假期：晚上８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"3203a66c1a98321d5ab36cb0cc3cb2e0fbbd24fc","tid":2409491,"uid":243351,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:19:43.000Z","msg":"行出街見到啲老人家 成日都有疑問 好想問佢地點解仲唔死  突別係坐係到 唔知做緊乜個啲  <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18afda4472ec3781719b3644c5c8ceac9054e762","tid":2409491,"uid":302347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3203a66c1a98321d5ab36cb0cc3cb2e0fbbd24fc","tid":2409491,"uid":243351,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:19:43.000Z","msg":"行出街見到啲老人家 成日都有疑問 好想問佢地點解仲唔死  突別係坐係到 唔知做緊乜個啲  <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:41:39.000Z","msg":"成日想40歲前死，唔甘心見到自己一直老落去殘落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ea0ebd0078c2423da37519e541e9e7270b7a12","tid":2409491,"uid":78769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T15:33:00.000Z","msg":"睇下係咩形式、方法"},{"pid":"3432d96d1987b6ede21323032e5ad878b74a7b11","tid":2409491,"uid":374394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T18:51:56.000Z","msg":"我絕對唔容許自己死喺其他人手上<br />\n只有我可以做低自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9898e49cf872d6541dfb45b6133e17158d80ec30","tid":2409491,"uid":343770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T21:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6bbb9d079460e4ceb01577f9c1af361bc3b44ba","tid":2409491,"ui